quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  51,43,"(Àmì tún wà) lára ìjọ Thamūd. (Rántí) nígbà tí A sọ fún wọn pé: “Ẹ jayé fún ìgbà díẹ̀ ná.”"
  51,44,"Wọ́n ṣègbéraga sí àṣẹ Olúwa wọn. Nítorí náà, iná láti ojú sánmọ̀ gbá wọn mú; wọ́n sì ń wò bọ̀ọ̀."
  51,45,"Wọn kò lè dìde nàró. Wọn kò sì lè ran ara wọn lọ́wọ́."
  52,34,"Kí àwọn náà mú ọ̀rọ̀ kan bí irú rẹ̀ wá tí wọ́n bá jẹ́ olódodo."
  52,35,"Tàbí wọ́n ṣẹ̀dá wọn láì sí Aṣẹ̀dá? Tàbí àwọn ni wọ́n ṣẹ̀dá ara wọn ni?"
  52,36,"Tàbí àwọn ni wọ́n ṣẹ̀dá àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀? Rárá o, wọn kò màmọ̀ dájú ni."
  53,28,"Kò sí ìmọ̀ kan fún wọn nípa rẹ̀. Wọn kò sì tẹ̀lé kiní kan bí kò ṣe àbá dídá. Dájúdájú àbá dídá kò sì níí rọrọ̀ kiní kan lára òdodo."
  53,29,"Nítorí náà, ṣẹ́rí kúrò ní ọ̀dọ̀ ẹni tó kẹ̀yìn sí ìrántí Wa, tí kò sì gbèrò kiní kan àfi ìṣẹ̀mí ayé."
  53,30,"Ìyẹn ni ohun tí wọ́n wọ̀n nínú ìmọ̀. Dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ lÓ nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa ẹni tó ṣìnà kúrò lójú ọ̀nà Rẹ̀. Ó sì nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa ẹni tó mọ̀nà."
  54,19,"Dájúdájú Àwa rán atẹ́gùn líle sí wọn ní ọjọ́ burúkú kan tó ń tẹ̀ síwájú.1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah Fussilat;  41:16.]
  54,20,"Ó ń fa àwọn ènìyàn tu bí ẹni pé kùkùté igi ọ̀pẹ tí wọ́n fà tu tegbòtegbò ni wọ́n."
  54,21,"Báwo ni ìyà Mi àti ìkìlọ̀ Mi ti rí ná (lára wọn)?"
  55,13,"Nítorí náà, èwo nínú àwọn ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa ẹ̀yin ènìyàn àti àlùjànnú ni ẹ máa pè ní irọ́?"
  55,14,"(Allāhu) ṣẹ̀dá ènìyàn láti ara amọ̀ gbígbẹ tó ń dún kokoko bí ìkòkò amọ̀."
  55,15,"Ó sì ṣẹ̀dá àlùjànnú láti ara ahọ́n iná tí kò ní èéfín."
  56,4,"Nígbà tí wọ́n bá mi ilẹ̀ tìtì ní mímìtìtì,"
  56,5,"àti nígbà tí Wọ́n bá fọ́ àwọn àpáta ní fífọ́ wómúwómú,"
  56,6,"- wọ́n sì máa di eruku àfẹ́dànù -"